<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="mt-5">
    <h1 class="title text-center">suggestive-giraffe</h1>
    <p class="lead text-center">Spice up your application with a bit of humour whilst improving communication and memorability. Go wild!</p>
    <a href="https://github.com/danobot/suggestive-giraffe" class="btn btn-default text-center">Github</a>
    <a href="https://github.com/danobot/suggestive-giraffe/issues/new" class="btn btn-default text-center">Submit Issue</a>
