    <div class="content mt-5">

      <p>This package generates <i>utterly ridiculous</i> identification strings like <span class="id-small">kinda-inappropriate-panda</span> and <span class="id-small">suggestive-giraffe</span>. Other honorable mentions include <span class="id">{{id.[0]}}</span> and of course <span class="id">{{id.[1]}}</span>. Only a <span class="id">{{id.[2]}}</span> could think of these!</p>
      <p>The maximum mapping space currently contains <span class="id-small">{{count}}million identifiers</span>. Use with caution, just like an <span class="id-small">extremely-cautious-pink-elephant</span> would! Uniqueness is not guaranteed. Your application should handle validations. Here are some random ones:</p>

      <div class="list row mb-5 mt-4 text-center">
        <div class="col-lg">
          <h2>Long <small>{{count}}M ids</small></h2>
          {{#each long}}
          <span class="id-small">{{this}}</span><br>

          {{/each}}

        </div>
        <div class="col-lg">
          <h2>Medium <small>{{countMedium}} ids</small></h2>
          {{#each medium}}
          <span class="id-small">{{this}}</span><br>

          {{/each}}

        </div>
        <div class="col-lg">
          <h2>Short <small>{{countShort}} ids</small></h2>
          {{#each short}}
          <span class="id-small">{{this}}</span><br>

          {{/each}}

        </div>
      </div>

      <p>Refresh and enjoy!</p>

      <p><small>Don't be an <span class="id-small">utterly-misinformed-antelope</span> and <a href="https://danielha.tk">stay in the loop</a>.</small></p>
